df.columns = df.columns.str.strip()
df['Prev. High Date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Prev. High Date'], errors='coerce')
df['Prev. High Month'] = df['Prev. High Date'].dt.month
df['Prev. High Year'] = df['Prev. High Date'].dt.year

df['Distance_from_High'] = df['LTP'] - df['New 52W/H price']
df['Pct_change_from_prev_high'] = ((df['New 52W/H price'] - df['Prev.High']) / df['Prev.High']) * 100
